as intergalactic star fighters.

78
00:03:15,278 --> 00:03:16,279
Vrroom!

79
00:03:18,782 --> 00:03:21,326
Oh, Richie, thank you for flying me in.

80
00:03:21,409 --> 00:03:23,787
Well, we wanted you to be hereto celebrate the big news.

81
00:03:23,871 --> 00:03:25,873
Dad got a job!

82
00:03:25,956 --> 00:03:26,874
Hey!

83
00:03:26,957 --> 00:03:28,291
