88
00:03:39,094 --> 00:03:40,679
It all plays right here.

89
00:03:40,762 --> 00:03:43,264
I know. I still can't believe it myself.

90
00:03:43,348 --> 00:03:45,184
Is he a crossing guard?

91
00:03:45,266 --> 00:03:46,643
Toll booth operator?

92
00:03:46,727 --> 00:03:48,687
Uh, crossing guard?

93
00:03:48,770 --> 00:03:50,564
He's a walrus!

94
00:03:50,647 --> 00:03:53,067
Ah! His dream job.

95
00:03:53,150 --> 00:03:55,610
