100
00:04:12,878 --> 00:04:15,130
They're not his, they're mine.

101
00:04:15,214 --> 00:04:16,757
Although he did pay for them.

102
00:04:16,840 --> 00:04:19,051
Why do you need all these clothes?

103
00:04:19,134 --> 00:04:21,053
