104
00:04:21,136 --> 00:04:23,388
Business Murray and fun Murray.

105
00:04:23,471 --> 00:04:25,432
Which one am I looking at now?

106
00:04:25,515 --> 00:04:27,392
Fun Murray.

107
00:04:27,475 --> 00:04:30,145
You don't understand.

108
00:04:30,229 --> 00:04:32,689
That's because I'm fun Murray right now.

109
00:04:38,237 --> 00:04:40,655
Let's get down to business.

110
00:04:40,739 --> 00:04:42,866
I don't have time for this.

111
00:04:42,950 --> 00:04:45,160
I'm in the middle of a fashion emergency.

112
00:04:45,244 --> 00:04:48,163
All of these clothes are unoriginal.

113
00:04:48,247 --> 00:04:51,750
