114
00:04:51,833 --> 00:04:54,836
Ooh, I have an idea for a unique belt.

115
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:58,548
How about you wear the anchor
chain from Richie's yacht?

116
00:04:58,632 --> 00:05:01,635
Come on, let's go take a stroll off the pier.

117
00:05:01,718 --> 00:05:03,095
Wait.

118
00:05:03,178 --> 00:05:04,554
I just had a breakthrough.

119
00:05:04,638 --> 00:05:06,848
I think I'm done shopping.

120
00:05:06,932 --> 00:05:10,978
Darcy, if you're serious, I will kiss you.

121
00:05:11,061 --> 00:05:12,562
Or not kiss you!

122
00:05:12,646 --> 00:05:15,149
Whichever makes you more likelyto never shop again.

123
00:05:15,232 --> 00:05:17,358
We're not kissing.

124
00:05:17,442 --> 00:05:18,359
But I'm serious.

125
00:05:18,443 --> 00:05:19,611
I'm done shopping.

126
00:05:19,694 --> 00:05:20,946
Yes!

127
00:05:21,029 --> 00:05:22,572
I'm hiring a personal fashion designer

128
00:05:22,656 --> 00:05:24,950
to handcraft my outfit every day.

129
00:05:25,033 --> 00:05:27,911
No!

130
00:05:27,995 --> 00:05:29,288
Irona!

131
00:05:32,124 --> 00:05:34,001
I am right here, Murray.

132
00:05:34,084 --> 00:05:36,419
I think it's time I teach Darcy a lesson

133
00:05:36,503 --> 00:05:39,547
about her reckless spending.

134
00:05:39,631 --> 00:05:42,592
I need you to intercept Darcy's call.

135
00:05:42,676 --> 00:05:44,928
I am sorry, but I can only accept commands

136
00:05:45,012 --> 00:05:46,680
from master Richie.

137
00:05:46,763 --> 00:05:51,143
Oh, well, Richie asked me to tell you.

138
00:05:51,226 --> 00:05:53,478
How do I know you're telling the truth?

139
00:05:53,561 --> 00:05:55,897
Because when I lie, I sneeze.

140
00:05:55,981 --> 00:05:57,899
[sneezes]

141
00:05:57,983 --> 00:06:00,735
That was just a coincidence.

142
00:06:00,819 --> 00:06:02,196
What can I do for you, Murray?

143
00:06:02,279 --> 00:06:04,405
Use your voice modulation software

144
00:06:04,489 --> 00:06:06,616
to pose as a fashion designer.

145
00:06:06,700 --> 00:06:09,244
I am sorry, but for security reasons, I cannot--

146
00:06:09,328 --> 00:06:11,496
Richie asked me to tell you.

147
00:06:11,579 --> 00:06:12,622
Right away.

148
00:06:12,706 --> 00:06:15,834
Hello, dahling!

149
00:06:18,503 --> 00:06:21,298
So you're a famous fashion designer?

150
00:06:21,380 --> 00:06:22,841
