245
00:10:55,029 --> 00:10:58,825
Is coshen "shoushin obloshin
bloshen" dollarsh a day.

246
00:10:58,908 --> 00:11:00,452
Darcy!

247
00:11:00,535 --> 00:11:03,455
How could you spend a shoushin
obloshin bloshen dollars

248
00:11:03,538 --> 00:11:04,998
of Richie's a day?

249
00:11:05,081 --> 00:11:07,334
