250
00:11:07,417 --> 00:11:09,669
She has to put the finishing
touches on this outfit,

251
00:11:09,752 --> 00:11:11,254
and then--

252
00:11:11,338 --> 00:11:12,880
what did you say you had to do?

253
00:11:12,964 --> 00:11:14,424
Dust.

254
00:11:14,508 --> 00:11:18,719
I mean fa-shion!

255
00:11:18,803 --> 00:11:20,805
Well, I can't wait to see you wear

256
00:11:20,888 --> 00:11:25,768
that not-ridiculous outfit in public.

257
00:11:25,852 --> 00:11:27,270
Keep up the good work.

258
00:11:27,354 --> 00:11:28,771
I can only keep up the good work--

259
00:11:28,855 --> 00:11:30,398
Richie says keep it up.

260
00:11:33,234 --> 00:11:35,278
